statements.sql: select count(id) as total from  (SELECT @row_no:=@row_no+1 as row_no, a.id ,a.name,a.mobile,a.sex,a.post ,a.sfz,CONCAT('[',a.institution_id ,']',b.name) as institution_name  FROM admin_employees a ,(select  @row_no:=0) t  ,admin_institutions b where a.institution_id=b.id and b.id in(2,8,9,10) ) z
